ing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"added","text":"New Nevaris map: expanded, prettier, and more optimised (part of ongoing world map refresh by @Polliwagon)","tags":[],"url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-added-9","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"added","text":"Boss lure crafting: craftsman NPC can craft boss lures in exchange for monster memories","tags":["crafting","boss"],"url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-added-10","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"added","text":"Vending Search: buy items in stacks of 10 or 100 (hold Ctrl or Shift respectively)","tags":[],"url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-added-11","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"added","text":"New Server Selection UI with region indicators","tags":[],"url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-added-12","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"added","text":"Click to Move toggle: disables the default click/hold-to-move character movement","tags":[],"url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-0","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Essence rarity order changed to Flow > Growth > Destruction > Rebirth > Chaos (rebalances Chaos imbalance)","tags":[],"url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-1","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Chaos essence: implicit swap removed \u2014 higher chance for other options, much lower chance of nothing happening on non-weapons","tags":[],"url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-2","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Rebirth essence: can now lock a stat while randomising the others (additional use case alongside original re-roll)","tags":[],"url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-chan