r 10% HP per second when out of combat (was 100% HP instantly)","tags":[],"url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-12","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Shadow Step: cooldown 2 \u2192 7 seconds (\u22121 per skill level)","tags":[],"url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-13","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Sniper Shot: damage 150% \u2192 200%","tags":[],"url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-14","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Bosses: faster cast times, adjusted cooldowns, more targeted attacks, now spawn giant minions","tags":[],"url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-15","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Shadow Step, Fireball, Ice Shard, Damnation, HolyWrath, Piercing Shot, and Sniper Shot can now be cast as either targeted or ground-targeted","tags":[],"url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-16","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Utility items: Def/MDef stats replaced with weight limit per refine","tags":[],"url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-17","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Monster flat Def scaling reduced: VIT/2 \u2192 VIT/5 (less impact on classes like Gunslinger)","tags":[],"url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-18","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Atk% is now a separate multiplier (slightly more effective than before)","tags":[],"url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-19","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Loot UI: moved and no longer clickable","tags":[],"url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-20","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Cursor is now frozen during drag-rotation","tags":[],"url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-removed-0","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"removed","text":"Hidden 100% Multistrike removed from Naga, Bat, and Wolf gear","tags":[],"url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-fixed-0","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"fixed","text":"Skill mods not applying to summons","tags":[],"url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-fixed-1","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"fixed","text":"Sacred Aegis not being refreshed correctly","tags":[],"url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-fixed-2","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"fixed","text":"Several issues with monster leap attacks","tags":[],"url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"}]}